<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٠ - <span class="c2">(٢٣٢٣)</span> وَحَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2591">أَبُو الرَّبِيعِ الْعَتَكِيُّ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1262">وَحَامِدُ بْنُ عُمَرَ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5112">وَأَبُو كَامِلٍ </a>قَالُوا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1619">حَمَّادٌ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1041">ثَابِتٍ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a>- بِنَحْوِهِ .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>